> This "feature" is restricted at present to a few pairs of variables that are
> hardwired at compile time.  They include:
> 
> CDPATH	cdpath
> FPATH		fpath
> MAILPATH	mailpath
> MANPATH	manpath
> PATH		path
> 
> These are documented in `man zshparam` and in the info files.  The remark
